{
  "id": "RAW_55a3bf",
  "title": "海外用户付费率超国内 3 倍，AI 出海应用增速领跑全球",
  "url": "http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&mid=2650670737&idx=4&sn=804ef5346f23ab573576f7546901f276",
  "date": "2025-05-20 14:01:00",
  "author": "gogo",
  "siteName": "白鲸出海",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom:-2.25em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:5px;\">\n     <section style=\"padding: 10px;margin-bottom: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <section style=\"font-size: 17px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-align: justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在全球人工智能生成内容（AIGC）技术爆发式增长的背景下，中国 AI 企业正以前所未有的速度重塑全球市场格局。有最新数据显示，2025 年 Q1 全球 AI 应用月活跃用户达 6.66 亿，同比增长 24.64%；其中 DeepSeek 凭借 1688% 的增速，市场份额从 0.7% 跃升至 7.9%，成为全球市场最大黑马。</span></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: auto;width: 2.25em;height: 2.25em;border-right: 5px solid rgb(5, 215, 250);border-bottom: 5px solid rgb(5, 215, 250);box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 0;\">\n     <strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></strong>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">本次报告的内容由广大大数据研究院整理发布，以下为报告核心内容摘要，助您洞悉 AIGC 领域的最新动态与未来机遇。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e8ea43-3f4f-4907-8942-dc03ea687e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;width:614px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503184998\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e8ea43-3f4f-4907-8942-dc03ea687e00/public\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\">AIGC应用全球市场现状：</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\">中国技术崛起，海外付费成熟</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">1、市场规模对比</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">国内市场：2024 年用户量达 1.35 亿，日均 Token 设置量激增 320 倍，AI 渗透率从 7% 提升至 27.1%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">海外市场：北美贡献 47% 收入，印度占据全球下载量 21%，预计全年收入 33 亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2ab80f53-f815-4204-709b-826f301af500/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5509259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 590px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100035814\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2ab80f53-f815-4204-709b-826f301af500/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">2、用户与商业化差异</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">国内用户：男性占比 60%+，聚焦工作学习场景，付费率低（66.8% 用户月均付费≤20 元）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">海外用户：年轻群体（18-35 岁占 70%）主导，娱乐与工具需求并重，订阅制模式成熟。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e8ea43-3f4f-4907-8942-dc03ea687e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;width:614px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503184998\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e8ea43-3f4f-4907-8942-dc03ea687e00/public\"></span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\">海外营销观察：视频创意主导，</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\">日韩市场潜力凸显</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI 应用在投放上并不如其他赛道那样大刀阔斧，更多是走的精细化路线，且头部效应明显，AI 广告主平均月均素材量仅 403 条，同比降幅 50.37%。 所有创意中，视频广告占比超过 83.46%，主要以功能展示为主，其中 15-30 秒短时长素材最受青睐（占比 50%+）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/677f8fa2-de7a-41f3-d1cd-b89340da1400/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 590px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100035810\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/677f8fa2-de7a-41f3-d1cd-b89340da1400/public\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在地区选择上，美国的广告主数量与总素材量都位居榜首；AI 应用的整体素材量在 2025Q1 迎来了全面提升，其中日本地区涨幅最大（同比 +157.9%），韩国地区紧随其后，该增长主要为本地化需求驱动。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 32px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/16a305df-fbad-4024-d8e4-73fd7c928400/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 590px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100035811\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/16a305df-fbad-4024-d8e4-73fd7c928400/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e8ea43-3f4f-4907-8942-dc03ea687e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;width:614px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503184998\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e8ea43-3f4f-4907-8942-dc03ea687e00/public\"></span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:8px 8px 32px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\">爆款案例观察：中国AI应用出海风向标</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在本次报告中，我们也对当下的热门 AI 出海应用营销进行了解析，其中就有一举改写 AI 模型市场环境的 DeepSeek。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">DeepSeek（深度求索）是由中国杭州深度求索人工智能基础技术研究有限公司研发的通用人工智能技术体系，其核心产品包括 V3 基础模型和 R1 推理模型，以低成本（如 R1 训练成本仅 557.6 万美元）和高效能重塑 AI 竞争格局，被誉为中国 AI 技术崛起的代表。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e67807b-60ca-4631-880a-803189872800/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 590px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100035812\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e67807b-60ca-4631-880a-803189872800/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其热门创意选取了 KOL 推荐的模式，在视频中间还加入了许多和其他产品的成本和效能对比，体现自己的优势，最后加入英伟达 CEO 采访片段再次拔高品牌形象。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75e6cb0b-581d-4288-4898-2e2048ca6600/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"1.775\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"240\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 240px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100035816\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/75e6cb0b-581d-4288-4898-2e2048ca6600/public\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px 32px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">投放渠道：YouTube 展现估值：55K</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e8ea43-3f4f-4907-8942-dc03ea687e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;width:614px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503184998\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c4e8ea43-3f4f-4907-8942-dc03ea687e00/public\"></span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin:8px 8px 32px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;text-align:center;\">\n   <span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);\"><span leaf=\"\">未来趋势：本地化与创意成破局关键</span></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前来看，海外用户的付费意愿比起国内更高，在 DeepSeek 和 ChatGPT 等大厂的洗刷下，用户对 AI 的接受度也较前两年大幅提升，订阅模式潜力巨大；部分产品如效率工具、AI 聊天机器人等赛道可直接复制国内成功经验。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <section style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ef371b3-7164-4ad8-dde5-d54f0e6ab500/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5361111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 590px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100035817\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5ef371b3-7164-4ad8-dde5-d54f0e6ab500/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">但有利也有弊，海外部分地区也推出了相关 AI 政策，这也对出海企业提出了更高的要求；同时头部应用用户一般粘性较高，需要通过更精细的“超本地化内容”（如文化梗、方言）建立情感连接，才有更大机会脱颖而出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">关于 AI 应用的未来，INCYMO.AI 创始人兼 CEO Anna Zdorenko 也给出了她的独家观点：“付费转化的核心在于创意能否直击用户痛点，并通过数据驱动优化。用户愿为‘被看见’的体验买单——这要求 AI 服务的第一印象必须量身定制，而非泛泛而谈。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">总的来说，2025 年，AIGC 应用的竞争已从技术迭代升级为“精准营销+本地化运营”的双重较量。中国 AI 企业凭借技术突破与创意策略，正快速抢占海外市场高地，但需警惕政策风险与成本压力。未来，“情感共鸣”与“数据驱动” 将成为破局核心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"白鲸出海\" data-alias=\"baijingapp\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ibJzB4CZdSVVibzdMibwQtdwy8EQ0rVJQMzMeVwmH1kp7pjAaxE9wD77310Y6qUkUGkjGOuj0shFDnU7EYFicKIcXA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"白鲸出海，泛互联网出海服务平台，白鲸专注于具备互联网属性的行业、公司、产品和服务的出海，包括应用、游戏、电商、区块链、智能手机及硬件、旅游、网络文学、影视、动漫、教育、体育和金融等。\" data-id=\"MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin: 0px 8px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ab92695d-c767-4901-3e38-e2d789966100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.125\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"white-space: normal;text-align: center;width: 562.138px;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"72\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ab92695d-c767-4901-3e38-e2d789966100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-t